<promed@promedmail.org>
[With no international airport within easy reach, the most likely source of
infection is -- as the report states -- a person from a country where _P.
vivax_ is endemic, with some immunity, carrying gametocytes in his blood,
with few or no symptoms. - Mod.EP]
